@prcastro : Thanks for reporting this!  We just added a section to the issues template about checking the docs on `master` at https://pandas-docs.github.io/pandas-docs-travis.

If you look at the corresponding links for <a href="https://pandas-docs.github.io/pandas-docs-travis/generated/pandas.DataFrame.astype.html">DataFrame</a> and <a href="https://pandas-docs.github.io/pandas-docs-travis/generated/pandas.Series.astype.html">Series</a>, you will see that we have addressed your issue already üëç 

See #17203 for the changes.  Closing since this issue has already been resolved.  Will re-open if you have any other concerns related to the `copy` parameter.
